Personal journal
Taking the [[flame war]] to a lolcow's '''personal journal''' can cause a great escalation of drama as Livejournal pussies rally against the "invasion" of a public space and retaliations occur.  Trolling a personal journal is often a [[final solution]].

The sanctity of the personal journal for nerds is demonstrated by the length of its non-redirected [[Wikipedia:personal journal|article]] on [[TOW]].
